Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:55.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}攜手 鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:56.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無論幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:22:58.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}和你 和你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:22:59.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}建立的 羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:04.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不會再次分離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:04.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}sha-la-la♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:10.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的存在 讓世界染上色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:14.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管什麼日子 都能展開笑靨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:15.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}girl meets girl
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:18.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不再是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:23.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}身旁隨時都有 可靠的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:26.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Thank you! 之後也一直是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:32.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}永遠的My friend
